aca.org/taxonomy/pilgrimage"/>Pilgrimage</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/priests.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/priests"/>Priests</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/saints.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/saints"/>Saints</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/wandering.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/wandering"/>Wandering</a></li></ul><h4>Related person(s)</h4><ul><li><a href="/aggregate/person/74.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/person/74"/>
